<h3 id="plotting-my-eeg-data">Plotting my EEG data</h3>
<p>(in SuperCollider)
<img src="../assets/img/20191026-cambridge-festival-of-ideas-03.jpg" alt="" />
<br />
<br />
Plot meanings:</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <p>row 1: theta median FZ (grey) with threshold on 1.5 microVolts (black)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>row 2: levels (blue triangles), theta median above threshold (green going down)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>row 3: theta median above threshold in % (green steps)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>row 4: theta median on P3 and P4 and their coherence below (green)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>row 5: theta median on F4 and P4 and their coherence below (green)
<br />
